      "description": "Offered is a driver-focused E46 M3 featuring the legendary S54B32 power plant. This high-revving straight-six remains mechanically sound with crisp throttle response via its factory individual throttle bodies. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission provides tactile engagement, delivering power to the rear wheels through a variable M-differential lock. Notable maintenance includes a recent VANOS overhaul and proactive subframe reinforcement, addressing common chassis fatigue points. Suspension geometry remains tight, utilizing MacPherson struts up front and a multi-link rear setup for superior lateral grip. While showing honest patina consistent with its age, the car\u2019s performance envelope remains fully intact, offering an unadulterated analog driving experience.",
